ot the most romantic thing that’s ever come out of his mouth, no, but they did settle on a friends with benefits kind of relationship—even if Childe’s stupid feelings have already gone way past that. \r\n\r\nZhongli takes a few more seconds to regain his breath, weakly shaking his head. “Not today... You have your meeting with Ningguang.”\r\n\r\nChuckling, Childe brushes back the strands of hair sticking onto Zhongli’s forehead. Gods, with the amount of times they had sex last night, both of them are filthy… \r\n\r\n“Alright, but we should get cleaned up first. How about we take a bath together?” Childe suggests.\r\n\r\nAt this, Zhongli purses his lips together. “I’m not naive, Childe. I know you will not stop at just bathing.”\r\n\r\nOuch. Childe clutches at his chest and feigns a gasp. “Zhongli-xiansheng, you must think so low of me… I was only suggesting it to save some time, considering this meeting with Ningguang is clearly very important… We shouldn’t miss that, should we?”\r\n\r\nZhongli doesn’t entertain him with a response, instead rising from Childe’s lap and slipping into a silk robe. Sighing, Childe lounges back on the bed and watches as Zhongli ties the robe around himself. It does very little to hide the numerous marks all over his body. \r\n\r\n“How did you know how to suck dick like that?” Childe asks, suddenly curious. “You continue to surprise me every time, xiansheng.”\r\n\r\nZhongli stops to think, tapping his chin as he gazes up at the ceiling in thought. “I have read books in the past that explored various sexual practices… As I recall, oral sex is supposed to be very pleasurable for both men and women.”\r\n\r\nSo, basically, Rex Lapis somehow stumbled across a section in the library full of erotic literature and decided to spend his benevolent spare time reading these for research. The life of an Archon is truly full of surprises. \r\n\r\n“I hope that was satisfactory for you,” Zhongli says, standing up straight with all the grace in the world